bsp;</span></p><ul><li style=3D"font-weight: 400;" aria-level=3D"1"><span s=
tyle=3D"font-weight: 400;">In Variation 1, you use the word =E2=80=98guaran=
tee=E2=80=99 in your main headline and notice a 35% uplift in conversions.&=
nbsp;</span></li><li style=3D"font-weight: 400;" aria-level=3D"1"><span sty=
le=3D"font-weight: 400;">In Variation 2, you include customer testimonials =
