 conversions.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=3D"font-weight: 400;" aria-level=
=3D"1"><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">In Variation 3, you add membership=
 trust signals and trust by association and get a 38% uplift in submissions=
.</span></li></ul><p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">All V1, V2, and V3 a=
re winners and showed an uplift in conversions.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span st=
yle=3D"font-weight: 400;">In such cases, you can combine all the winning id=
